' =============================================================================
' GTNH Platform — User Flow: System & Network
' 3 диаграммы: startup sequence, service communication, multiplayer sync
' =============================================================================

' ===========================================================================
' 1. Startup Sequence (order matters)
' ===========================================================================
@startuml system-startup
title **Flow S1: Startup Sequence (порядок запуска)**

participant "MessageRouter\n(Go)" as MR
participant "ChunkStore\n(C++)" as CS
participant "WorldGenerator\n(C++)" as WG
participant "EntityStateStore\n(C++)" as ESS
participant "PipeNetwork\n(C++)" as PN
participant "SimulationCore\n(C++)" as Sim
participant "MetaDB\n(Go)" as MDB
participant "Gateway\n(C++)" as GW
participant "GameClient\n(C++)" as Client

== Фаза 1: Базовые сервисы ==

MR -> MR: Start pub/sub broker
note right: Internal pub/sub, heartbeat, discovery
MR -> MR: Init priority channels system

== Фаза 2: Хранилища ==

note over CS: Загрузка LMDB, проверка целостности
CS -> MR: Register chunkd service
CS -> MR: Subscribe: world.chunks.get

note over ESS: Загрузка LMDB для entity state
ESS -> MR: Register ess service
ESS -> MR: Subscribe: entity.state.get/set

note over MDB: Инициализация SQLite
MDB -> MR: Register metadb service

== Фаза 3: Вычисления ==

note over WG: Init FastNoiseLite
WG -> MR: Register world_generator service
WG -> MR: Subscribe: world.generator.generate

note over PN: Init pipe graph
PN -> MR: Register pipe_network service

== Фаза 4: Simulation ==

note over Sim: Init ECS registry + systems
Sim -> Sim: Register 20 Hz tick loop
Sim -> MR: Register simcore service
Sim -> MR: Subscribe: world.blocks.changed
Sim -> MR: Subscribe: sim.craft.request
Sim -> MR: Subscribe: player.inventory.actions

== Фаза 5: Шлюз ==

note over GW: Init io_uring, listen on TCP port
GW -> MR: Register gateway service
GW -> MR: Subscribe: all client-facing topics

== Фаза 6: Клиент ==

note over Client: bgfx init, GLFW window
Client -> GW: TCP connect (FlatBuffers)
GW -> Client: Welcome + initial state
Client -> Client: Request initial chunks

@enduml

' ===========================================================================
' 2. Cross-Service Communication Patterns
' ===========================================================================
@startuml system-service-communication
title **Flow S2: Cross-Service Communication Patterns**

participant "Service A\n(Publisher)" as Pub
participant "MessageRouter\n(Go)" as MR
participant "Service B\n(Subscriber)" as Sub1
participant "Service C\n(Subscriber)" as Sub2

== Pattern 1: Pub/Sub (1-to-N) ==

Pub -> MR: Publish topic.data
MR -> MR: Fan-out to subscribers
MR -> Sub1: Deliver topic.data
MR -> Sub2: Deliver topic.data

note right #8E44AD
  Пример: world.blocks.changed
  Published by: ChunkStore
  Subscribed by: SimulationCore, Gateway
end note

== Pattern 2: RPC (Request-Response) ==

Sub1 -> MR: RPC: service.method
MR -> Pub: Forward RPC
Pub -> Pub: Process
Pub -> MR: Return result
MR -> Sub1: Deliver response

note right #27AE60
  Пример: SetBlockMeta
  Caller: SimulationCore
  Executor: ChunkStore
end note

== Pattern 3: Chained Pub/Sub ==

Pub -> MR: Publish event
MR -> Sub1: Forward event
Sub1 -> Sub1: Process, emit new event
Sub1 -> MR: Publish derived.event
MR -> Sub2: Forward derived.event

note right
  Пример:
  ChunkStore -> world.blocks.changed
  SimulationCore -> sim.multiblock.created
end note

== Pattern 4: Priority Channels ==

Pub -> MR: Publish urgent.topic
note right: Высокий приоритет (system health)
MR -> MR: Queue by priority
MR -> Sub1: Deliver urgent first
MR -> Sub2: Deliver urgent first

@enduml

' ===========================================================================
' 3. Multiplayer Sync
' ===========================================================================
@startuml system-multiplayer-sync
title **Flow S3: Multiplayer Sync (несколько клиентов)**

actor "Player 1" as P1
actor "Player 2" as P2
participant "Client 1" as C1
participant "Client 2" as C2
participant "Gateway" as GW
participant "MessageRouter" as MR
participant "SimulationCore" as Sim
participant "ChunkStore" as CS

== Player 1 ставит блок ==

P1 -> C1: Размещает блок
C1 -> GW: SetBlockAction(pos, block_id)
GW -> MR: Publish world.blocks.set
MR -> CS: SetBlock
CS -> MR: Publish world.blocks.changed

par Синхронизация
    MR -> Sim: onBlockChanged(pos, block_id)
    Sim -> Sim: Update ECS, check multiblock
    Sim -> MR: Publish sim.blockentity.update (if needed)

    MR -> GW: Relay to all connected clients

    GW -> C1: BlockUpdate (source)
    GW -> C2: BlockUpdate (broadcast)
    C1 -> P1: Показывает блок
    C2 -> P2: Показывает блок (другого игрока)
end

== Player 2 видит изменение ==

note right #9B59B6
  Все изменения мира
  бродкастятся всем клиентам
  через Gateway.
  Никакой peer-to-peer.
end note

== Player 1 уходит (disconnect) ==

P1 -> C1: Disconnect / закрывает игру
C1 -> GW: TCP disconnect
GW -> GW: Clean up connection state
GW -> MR: Publish player.disconnected

MR -> Sim: onPlayerDisconnected(player_id)
Sim -> Sim: Free player-bound ECS entities

note right
  SimulationCore продолжает
  работу без игрока.
  Автокрафты и буры
  работают в обычном режиме.
end note

MR -> C2: Broadcast: player 1 disconnected
C2 -> P2: P1 vanished from world

== Player 1 подключается снова (reconnect) ==

P1 -> C1: Запускает клиент, подключается
C1 -> GW: TCP connect
GW -> C1: Welcome, current generation
C1 -> GW: Request chunks around login pos
GW -> MR: Publish player.reconnected
MR -> Sim: onPlayerReconnected(player_id)
Sim -> Sim: Load player ECS state from MetaDB

note right
  Reconnect:
  - Client gets latest chunk data
  - Gets current machine states
  - Sees any autonomous progress
  - Все автокрафты/буры видны
end note

@enduml
